# Project Structure

Design documents for this project are located in `docs/DesignDocument/`.

Key documents include:
- `docs/DesignDocument/BD.md` - Business Design / main design document
- `docs/DesignDocument/SR.md` - System Requirements
- `docs/DesignDocument/CLI-sample.md` - CLI usage examples

Refer to these documents when discussing architecture, requirements, or design decisions.
